<h2 id="using-nipe">Using Nipe</h2>

<h3 id="download-and-install">Download and install:</h3>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>    <span class="c"># Download</span>
    <span class="nv">$ </span>git clone https://github.com/GouveaHeitor/nipe
    <span class="nv">$ </span><span class="nb">cd </span>nipe

    <span class="c"># Automatic installation</span>
    <span class="nv">$ </span><span class="nb">chmod</span> +x setup.sh
    <span class="nv">$ </span>./setup.sh
    
    <span class="c"># Manual installation</span>
    <span class="nv">$ </span>cpan <span class="nb">install </span>Switch JSON LWP::UserAgent Config::Simple
    <span class="nv">$ </span>perl nipe.pl <span class="nb">install</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h3 id="commands">Commands:</h3>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>    COMMAND          FUNCTION
    <span class="nb">install          </span>Install dependencies
    start            Start routing
    stop             Stop routing
    restart          Restart the Nipe process
    status           See status

    Examples:

    perl nipe.pl <span class="nb">install
    </span>perl nipe.pl start
    perl nipe.pl stop
    perl nipe.pl restart
    perl nipe.pl status
</code></pre></div></div>

